Educational Use and Dataset Notice

Copyright (c) 2026 Marco

This repository is provided as an Artificial Intelligence Applications course
project release.

The source code may be inspected, executed, and adapted for educational review
and non-commercial coursework purposes.

The included test images, presentation files, paper figures, and result images
are provided only for evaluating this course project. They should not be reused,
redistributed, or republished outside the course/project context without
permission from the image owners and project team.

Large third-party model weights are not included. SAM and YOLO model weights
must be downloaded from their respective official sources and used according to
their original licenses and terms.
